Company Overview of Delaware Group Limited-Term Government Funds - Delaware Limited-Term Diversified Income Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Delaware Group Limited-Term Government Funds - Delaware Limited-Term Diversified Income Fund is an open-ended fixed income mutual fund launched by Delaware Management Holdings, Inc. It is managed by Delaware Management Business Trust. The fund invests in fixed income markets of the United States. It invests in investment grade fixed-income securities including securities issued or guaranteed by the U.S. government, its agencies or instrumentalities, securities issued by U.S. corporations including bonds, notes, debentures, and commercial paper of U.S. companies rated at least BBB- or higher by S&P or Baa3 or higher by Moody's. The Fund seeks to maintain an average duration of one to three ye...
Delaware Group Limited-Term Government Funds - Delaware Limited-Term Diversified Income Fund is an open-ended fixed income mutual fund launched by Delaware Management Holdings, Inc. It is managed by Delaware Management Business Trust. The fund invests in fixed income markets of the United States. It invests in investment grade fixed-income securities including securities issued or guaranteed by the U.S. government, its agencies or instrumentalities, securities issued by U.S. corporations including bonds, notes, debentures, and commercial paper of U.S. companies rated at least BBB- or higher by S&P or Baa3 or higher by Moody's. The Fund seeks to maintain an average duration of one to three years. It employs factors such as economic and market condition to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Barclays 1–3 Year U.S. Government/Credit Index. It was formerly known as Delaware Limited Term Government Fund - Delaware Limited-Term Diversified Income Fund. Delaware Group Limited-Term Government Funds - Delaware Limited-Term Diversified Income Fund was formed on November 24, 1985 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


